data.description: **Seller will contribute up to $5000.00 in closing costs**This manufactured home has it all! Situated in a quiet neighborhood, this home offers plenty of parking space and is set on a little over half an acre. Spend time outdoors under the large 41x12 covered back patio or relax by the inground pool, which needs to be serviced and cleaned. Enjoy open and airy indoor and outdoor spaces perfect for entertaining guests. With new windows, vinyl plank waterproof flooring, and a two-year-old roof with a 10-year warranty, you'll have peace of mind knowing your home will remain in great condition. Inside, the open floor plan is perfect for family gatherings and features wainscoting in main areas. Take advantage of the generous storage spaces, walk-in closets, laundry room with washer and dryer and brand-new electrical outlets throughout. Additional storage shed in backyard. The master bathroom has a spacious garden tub with separate shower and double vanity. The kitchen features large windows, a garbage disposal, an abundance of storage, and snack bar. Don't let this opportunity pass you by! Come see it for yourself! This home won't last long-Schedule your personal showing and make this house your own!
